name: Lost in Space
description: An original photograph by Waytoomad. Collectors who own 10 or more editions of 'Lost in Space' will receive this photograph's physical/metal print. The number of editions you own determines the size of the print you receive: 10 editions = 8" x 12" print, 15 editions = 12" x 18" print, and 20 editions = 16" x 24" print. Once 10 or more editions are collected, please reach out on twitter @_waytoomad.
